title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map rules
description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export the data in the table, an exception occurs at the function ReportEngineService.getMetaData().
EB: The export should successfully export the data from the table.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
